longBusinessSummary: Pekin Life Insurance Company operates as a life and accident, and health insurance company in the United States. The company offers auto and home insurance products; life insurance products, annuities, and funeral preplanning products; health insurance products; and business insurance products, including business auto, business property, general liability, and workers compensation insurance products. It also provides group life, dental, and short-term disability, as well as voluntary products and medicare supplements. It sells its insurance products primarily through independent agents. The company was founded in 1921 and is headquartered in Pekin, Illinois. Pekin Life Insurance Company operates as a subsidiary of Farmers Automobile Insurance Association.
